Configuration:

libccid loads the '/ifd-ccid.bundle/Contents/Info.plist" file, which can be
made available from a ROM module in the VFS of the application:

<config>
	<libc>
		<vfs>
			<dir name="ifd-ccid.bundle">
				<dir name="Contents">
					<rom name="Info.plist"/>
				</dir>
			</dir>
		</vfs>
	</libc>
</config>
